text: Rafał Choynowski (born 23 June 1960) is a Polish equestrian. He competed in the team eventing at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:Polish male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Poland Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Poznań
